Class Entity

java.lang.Object
java.util.Observable
jbubblebobble.model.entity.Entity
Direct Known Subclasses:
Bubble, Enemy, EnemyBubble, Player, PowerUp
public abstract class Entity extends Observable
Entity class is the superclass of all the entities in the game

    • handleEntityCollision

      protected abstract void handleEntityCollision(Entity entity)
      Handle entity collision performs routines when an entity collides with another entity. The routine is different for each entity. The method is abstract and must be implemented by the subclasses.
      Parameters:
      entity - the entity

    • handleWallCollision

      protected abstract void handleWallCollision(Wall wall)
